SO... last week was lots of fun... working on float and what not and going to mals house stubbing my toe and having it bleed all over the place. Well I will start with friday because thats basically the farthest back that i remember. Friday right after school i go to my car and hop in ready to drive home right... WRONG it wouldnt start. I tried to jump start it i tried everything nothing worked i was soooo pissed. Alex tried to help but o no it still didnt work. Lindsey Kemmsies my love tried to help me and whatever it was broke! so she took me home instead and since the plan got screwed up Allisons grandma had to come pick me her and Mal up at my house all the way from grossmont and takeus up to her aunts house in Lemon Grove. SO we thanked her for the ride and then we started helping get ready for the party!!! We all really were tired and so we were out by 1030 but my mom called me at 230 in the morning and so i talked to her for a lil... yeah were odd. Then Saturday we went shopping and i found the cutest purse o yeah way cuter then all the rest what now BiTCH! haha so i didnt spend NE money which was really hard for me. Allisons aunt, the sweetest person ever, bought me a lip gloss from mac and i love it its hott. then the party was that night so we were all getting ready, and what did i do? well allison and mallorie invited their boyfriends so i had to bring some1 and the person i really liked was unavailable so i asked... u guessed it MANNY. hmm what a mistake? o yeah so i dont really want to talk about the party like at all it was fun when all the guys left and we were dancing with no inhibitions (((ooo big word go me))) we all made about 58 dollars so it worked out pretty good... sunday was relax day yeah and today at school was cool i love michelle and sarah spanish is my favorite class after math even though i think that the teacher could jump off a cliff... o and apusg is my 2nd fave so spanish is really 3rd but whatever. But right now im just thinkin bout the boy who is on my mind lately and hes real fun so yeah love all of you!

Just freaking kidding!!!! So today i wake up and my moms like freaking out... what else is new? SO i came home watched a lil tv and took a nap, (yeah i am that cool) lol then i went to basketball and that sucked ummm 9 5 in 30's not fun!! and thanx Allison for pointing out this week is seven BiTCH lol... well i came home took a shower and then got all ready to watch Laguna Beach aww i love LC and Jason even though he is stupid sometimes... i wish all boys could be as sweet as him. Well some are but they are just sweet TaLKERS! which is no good so then i did some homework and now im doing this and im about to go to bed but i just have to say that i am lovin life right now... i do NOT know why lol but yeah o and my dad fixed my car so it works so no more PiMPiN MAMA VAN

So onto current stuff now:

 

 I <333 my new best friends... well i dont know if you can call them new since we've been like this since summer startwed and even part of last year. But anyways Mallorie and Allison mean the world to me. I think that i would go psycho without them telling me that "shes" a bitch and who cares about her and "hes" stupid dont like him they save me and everytime i dont listen to them something shitty happens i.e. JOSH and MANNY lol but whatever they like who i like now and thats all that matters right?

SOOO what happened this week??

MonDAY---Shit thats too long ago all I remember is that i wore the skirt that SARAH lent me p.s. I Love her too!

WednesDAY---I went out to lunch with pete and zach and it was lots of fun because they are pretty awesome and then i went to basketball and i was the only "big girl" there... yeah Im a big girl???

ThursDAY---Ummm I was really cool and i came home from school and took a nap...

FriDAY!!!---went to school came home during fonsatans class because lol well no need to go into boring details and then i went to submarina then i went back to school in time for lunch and after school Me Allison and Mallorie went SHOPPING for HALLOWEEN!!!! so much fun I wish wed have gotten the other booty shorts but whatever they all serve the same purpose... Haha we are goin to look so hott this friday i cant freakin wait!!

SaturDAY---slept in then i went to my best friend Lexxis house. She's a different kind of best friend shes like the one u have all thru lil kids till middle school then she gets the nerve to move all the way to el cajon and i dont get to see her that often but i still love her to death So we watched the Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants and just hung out for like 6 hours. She was on Vicadin because she just got her wisdom teeth removed. We had long talks about her college and my high school crap lol then i came home to get ready for Justins took a shower at like 5 and went to get Allison at 7 and we came back to my house and i said FUck my hair because it still wasnt dry so it went up into a HOTT messy bun lol We went to Justins I danced my lil heart out and omg I freakin love SARAH GIRTY AND KRISTI BROWN o and BRANDON and JESSALYN cuz i got to hang out with all those awesome people for a whole night it was great then me and allison came back to my house had a talk about some certain boys and watched the sisterhood of the traveling pants I <3 that movie!

Today--- was boring because all i did was wake up take allison home [[we got dippin dots on the way even tho its no where near her house]] and came home and relaxed all day so i got bored and decided to do this.
